textBox.richText: Woke up to only an inch or two at the house, but WP claimed 7. Ditched out early, got my first chair at 8:35. Did a lap through the bowl and kinikinick, then did a bunch of Bella laps. Snagged my jacket on a tree; had ski patrol help me patch it up with some athletic tape. Met up with Gunter around noon...did some Eagle Wind laps, then headed down to Pioneer, and did a bunch of the tree runs in there.
